<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 15:14:04 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>奥的斯因中美建筑活动放缓下调年度销售预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/otis-cuts-annual-sales-view-slowdown-construction-activity-china-us-2024-07-24/</link><description>由于北美和中国对其新设备的需求疲软，电梯制造商奥的斯环球公司 (Otis Worldwide) 周三下调了 2024 年净销售额预期。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 12:08:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/otis-cuts-annual-sales-view-slowdown-construction-activity-china-us-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>特使表示，日本将恢复对斯里兰卡停滞项目的资助</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-resume-funding-stalled-projects-sri-lanka-envoy-says-2024-07-24/</link><description>东京驻斯里兰卡特使周三表示，日本将恢复为斯里兰卡所有陷入停滞的项目提供资金，这是自该岛国与其官方债权人敲定 100 亿美元重组协议以来的首次此类声明。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 11:57:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-resume-funding-stalled-projects-sri-lanka-envoy-says-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，印度可能放松对部分中国投资的限制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-likely-ease-curbs-some-chinese-investments-sources-say-2024-07-24/</link><description>两位政府消息人士称，印度可能会放松对中国在太阳能电池板和电池制造等非敏感行业投资的限制，而新德里缺乏专业知识，这阻碍了国内制造业。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 10:48:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-likely-ease-curbs-some-chinese-investments-sources-say-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>早间出价：高收益酒吧，哈里斯民意调查上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-24/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 10:07:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>数据显示，中国比亚迪在新加坡和东南亚的电动汽车市场上扩大了对特斯拉的领先优势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-widens-ev-lead-over-tesla-singapore-southeast-asia-data-shows-2024-07-24/</link><description>政府数据显示，今年上半年，中国比亚迪在新加坡扩大了对特斯拉的销量领先优势，凸显了这家全球最大电动汽车制造商在中国竞争对手销量方面面临的挑战。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 09:00:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-widens-ev-lead-over-tesla-singapore-southeast-asia-data-shows-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>雷米首席财务官表示，尚未给出对中国白兰地调查做出决定的日期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/remy-cfo-says-no-date-yet-given-decision-china-brandy-probe-2024-07-24/</link><description>在顶级干邑生产商上周参加了有关该问题的听证会后，人头马君度首席财务官周三表示，北京方面尚未给出对欧盟白兰地反倾销调查做出决定的官方时间表。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 08:51:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/remy-cfo-says-no-date-yet-given-decision-china-brandy-probe-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯指责美国加剧北极紧张局势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-accuses-us-stoking-tensions-arctic-2024-07-24/</link><description>俄罗斯周三指责华盛顿加剧北极紧张局势，并驳斥了美国军方关于俄罗斯和中国在该地区加强合作可能影响地区稳定的说法。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 08:40:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-accuses-us-stoking-tensions-arctic-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾称与北京就南海问题达成“安排”，但没有对船只进行检查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-has-common-understanding-with-china-tensions-disputed-shoal-2024-07-24/</link><description>一名高级安全官员周三表示，菲律宾已与北京就向南海搁浅海军舰艇上的士兵执行补给任务达成协议，但不会接受中国的检查。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 08:35:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-has-common-understanding-with-china-tensions-disputed-shoal-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰告诉中国，如果莫斯科真诚行事，它愿意进行谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/ukraines-top-diplomat-meets-chinas-wang-yi-talks-guangzhou-2024-07-24/</link><description>乌克兰最高外交官周三在南部城市广州举行的会谈中告诉中国外交部长，如果莫斯科愿意真诚地进行谈判，基辅愿意与俄罗斯进行会谈，但他表示目前没有看到任何证据。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 07:25:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/ukraines-top-diplomat-meets-chinas-wang-yi-talks-guangzhou-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国详细介绍了扩大国家机密的法律，着眼于数据安全</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-details-expanded-law-state-secrets-eyeing-data-security-2024-07-24/</link><description>中国本周公布了修订后的《国家秘密法》的细节，该法改变了对政府官员处理机密信息的限制，禁止负责掌握国家秘密的人员未经批准出国。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 06:40:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-details-expanded-law-state-secrets-eyeing-data-security-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>保时捷下半年力争恢复产量并应对供应链风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/porsche-profits-drop-after-months-lower-sales-supply-chain-issues-2024-07-24/</link><description>保时捷周三表示，在经历了数月的供应链障碍、电动汽车需求放缓以及中国销量下滑之后，该公司正在努力恢复产量，并重新调整支出优先顺序，以打造更灵活的产品线。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 06:03:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/porsche-profits-drop-after-months-lower-sales-supply-chain-issues-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>东盟寻求解决缅甸危机和南海紧张局势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asean-seeks-tackle-myanmar-crisis-south-china-sea-tension-ministers-meet-laos-2024-07-24/</link><description>东南亚集团东盟周三在老挝举行会议，寻求推进陷入僵局的解决缅甸危机和缓和南中国海紧张局势的努力，而几天后，世界各大国的高级外交官将齐聚一堂。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 06:03:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asean-seeks-tackle-myanmar-crisis-south-china-sea-tension-ministers-meet-laos-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>Forvia因汽车需求低迷而下调前景，着眼于与中国汽车制造商进行交易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/forvia-trims-2024-outlook-lower-auto-demand-extra-costs-north-america-2024-07-24/</link><description>按收入计算，全球第七大汽车零部件供应商 Forvia 周三下调了销售额和利润率预期，原因是全球汽车需求低迷以及与墨西哥汽车内饰业务供应商发生纠纷，导致其股价下跌。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 05:35:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/forvia-trims-2024-outlook-lower-auto-demand-extra-costs-north-america-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾命令离岸博彩中心的外籍工人两个月内离开</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-orders-foreign-workers-offshore-gaming-hubs-leave-2-months-2024-07-24/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯决定取缔离岸赌博公司后，菲律宾移民局周三表示，该国已下令在离岸赌博公司工作的外国人在两个月内离开该国。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 05:25:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-orders-foreign-workers-offshore-gaming-hubs-leave-2-months-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>独家：LGES 正在与中国材料公司洽谈为欧洲生产低成本电动汽车电池</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/lg-energy-solution-talks-with-chinese-firms-make-low-cost-ev-batteries-europe-2024-07-24/</link><description>韩国 LG 能源解决方案公司 (LGES) 一位高管表示，正在与三个中国供应商就为欧洲生产低成本电动汽车电池进行谈判，欧盟对中国制造的电动汽车征收额外关税后，竞争将加剧。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 05:05:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/lg-energy-solution-talks-with-chinese-firms-make-low-cost-ev-batteries-europe-2024-07-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>